              "children": []
            },
            {
              "level": "c",
              "levelType": "lowercase",
              "text": "Water bodies occupying fault-bounded structural depressions: lakes and landlocked seas; inland seas with outlets to the oceans; elongated seas formed by crustal separation",
              "children": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
