              "text": "The oceanic crust",
              "children": []
            },
            {
              "level": "b",
              "levelType": "lowercase",
              "text": "Major features of the deep-ocean floor: oceanic ridges, aseismic ridges, trenches, fracture zones, and transform faults; seamounts and guyots; abyssal hills and plains; sediments of the ocean floor [see also G., below]",
